<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7584> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7584" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Pr. 59. See MRR 2.188. Presided over the trial of C. Antonius  (Cic. Vat. 27), apparently in the quaestio de repetundis (Schol. Bob. 94St), not de maiestate (see Gruen, Latomus 32, 1973, 301-310; cf. LGRR 288).\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4997> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4997" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Presided at the trial of C. Antonius, probably in the Quaestio do maiestate (Cic. Vat. 27; see 62, Promagistrates, on Antonius)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4982> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4982" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Appointed by decree of the Senate as ambassadors to induce various Gallic tribes not to join the Helvetii (Cic. Att. 1. 19. 2-3; cf. 1. 20.5). on Valerius, see Münzer, Gent. Val. 43, no. 28." .
